Revision history for Perl extension XML::Grove.

Backwards incompatible changes are marked with a `*'.

0.05  Thu Sep 24 08:30:43 MDT 1998
	- fixes
	  - test.pl wasn't updated for new XML::Parser and failed

0.04  Sun Sep 20 12:57:06 CDT 1998
	- Support for Clark Cooper's XML::Parser 2.x
	* $grove is now returned from $parser->parsefile instead of in
	  $parser->{Grove}.  $parser->{Grove} is still available when
	  using XML::Parser 0.0.
	- fixes
	  - my-html.pl: fix visit_name subs
	  - Iter::at_next, Iter::at_first: fixed (had always returned false)
	  - Iter::parent: now correctly returns parent iterator
	  - XML::Grove: Grove no longer ISA XML::Document (that's not
	    supported yet)
	  - XML::Grove::AsCanonXML: visit_pi had died calling wrong method
	  - XML::Grove::AsCanonXML: convert tab, nl, and cr to entities

0.03  Sat Apr 11 10:38:59 CDT 1998
	- XML::Grove::Visitor: returns results as a list
	- XML::Grove::AsString: rewrote using visitor module
	- XML::Grove::AsCanonXML: new module
	- fixes
	  - $element->attr may return a scalar: updated docs and fixed
	    Iter and Visitor to match

0.02  Sun Apr  5 12:10:10 CDT 1998
	- README updated
	- added examples for Iter and Visitor
	- XML::Grove::Visitor: new module
	- XML::Grove::Iter: new module
	- XML::Grove::AsString: new module
	- examples/dump.pl: renamed to examples/grove.pl
	- moved `as_string' to ::AsString
	- fixes
	  - examples/grove.pl: removed SGML simple-dump leftovers

0.01  Thu Apr  2 11:58:03 1998
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.18

